Looks like this will hold up for sometime to come. Plastic is thick and measuring cup is sturdy. Markings are clear and legible.Clear construction makes it especially easy to read. The one I had had the metric readings on the side you see when holding it in the right hand, but this is perfect. It may or may not last a lifetime, but at 80 years of age I am gambling it will.I really like this cup because it feels very strong and the measurements are very clear! The last plastic measuring cup that I bought on Amazon was very flimsy and most the measurement numbers disappeared after the fourth of fifth time I washed it! I like everything about this cup!💯🤟👏Use for my international baking needs, GREAT!!I bought this to use when changing the oil in my L&G small engines. The cup is strong and the level markings are good and easy to read.I like that it is two cups in size with ample room above the fill like. It is plastic, so it probably needs a little more care for durability, but I always hand wash mine as I use it, so it should last.I needed to measure some motor oil. I was fairly certain my wife wouldn't approve of me using her glass measuring cup from the kitchen.It's like a measuring cup we've all seen before. Very happy with it.Serves its purpose.Markings are distinct;
